node.text:
Whether strutting, blading, or dueting we’ve put our newest Sweat silhouette to the test. 

Finished with moisture-wicking fabric, a compressive waistband, and hidden pockets (!), these next-level leggings work just as hard as you do. 

Roll on over to the #LiveFlowSweatDuet challenge on TikTok #VSLiveFlowSweat
